WEBVTT

00:00,000 --> 00:04,950
What Actually Moves Outcomes

00:05,000 --> 00:09,950
If data is unclear, execution drifts even when the strategy looks solid on paper.

00:10,000 --> 00:14,950
Convert one recurring meeting into a decision review with explicit next actions.

00:15,000 --> 00:19,950
Run a compact loop: signal, decision, action, evidence, then adjust next cycle.

00:20,000 --> 00:24,950
This approach compounds because each cycle keeps what works and drops what does not.

00:25,000 --> 00:29,950
If the metric does not move after two cycles, simplify the process and retest.
